Homework 3 Board Game:
Dungeons and Dragons Style dice roll, turn based on a board, can go forward or backwards. The board layout is like shoots and ladders with the movement on a fixed track with possibility to move up and down to spots. 
Dice Roll: 1-20
Back or forward
Total Spots: 200
“Hill” and “Stair” positions
Down or up to a certain position
Player turns go in order (1,2,3,4,etc)
Start at 1 and End at 200
Each person takes turns

Functions: DiceRoll, LoadEvents, MovePlayer
